    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the info. i didnt realize the pH affected it like that. i'll get some soil test kits. besides the pH, is there anything else happening underground or in the soil structure that could be causing this? like maybe something wrong with the roots or the way the soil is breaking down?",
      "source": "evaluator",
